premise_source_doc_sentence: Victoria Leigh Blum  (  born October 15 , 1955  )  , known by the stage name Tanya Roberts , is an American actress and producer .
She is known for her role as Stacey Sutton in the James Bond film A View to a Kill  (  1985  )  , and as Midge Pinciotti on That '70s Show  (  1998 -- 2004  )  .
